ircularityLock circularityLock,\n            ClassLoader classLoader,\n            JavaModule module) {\n            return typeDescription;\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class DelegatingTestClassLoader extends ClassLoader {\n        DelegatingTestClassLoader(ClassLoader parent) {\n            super(parent);\n        }\n    }\n\n    public static class LoadedSuperType {\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 486, "output": 1240, "cacheRead": 17920, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 19646, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777444745577, "responseId": "resp_0cde37590e04d1360169f1a78a0428819191015af1a11ed9d9"}}
